title: OfficeSuite + PDF Editor Premium 9.8.14515 !{Latest}
description:
OfficeSuite + PDF Editor Premium 9.7.14188 !{Latest}

One of the best office packages for your Android device, you can download OfficeSuite below. You can work with the format MS Word and Excel, supports the work with documents such as PDF and PowerPoint.

 The program will allow you to view attachments to mail messages, and doing this will also be convenient as on a personal computer.

You can create your own document, spreadsheet and then send it to your friends. Here is the list of supported formats: DOC, DOCX, XLS, XLSX, PPT, PPTX, CSV, TXT, PDF, you can also work with ZIP archives.

What's new:
* NEW: OfficeSuite Drive - save your files to the cloud and use them across all your devices
* Use your camera to digitize and edit paper documents
* Look up words in dictionaries or the Web
* Added themes to presentations
* Copy images, shapes and annotations from PDFs to other documents
* Improved font support when exporting to PDF

License : ShareWare 
Size : 34 MB 
OS : Android 1.6 and higher
